      <title>백엔드 개발자의 Kubernetes 마스터 플랜 (CKA 취득 목표)</title>
      <link href="/2025/09/17/kubernetes-learning-roadmap/"/>
      <url>/2025/09/17/kubernetes-learning-roadmap/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>체계적인 Kubernetes 학습으로 CKA 취득하고 실무에서 바로 써먹을 수 있는 로드맵</p></blockquote><h2 id="🎯-목표-설정"><a href="#🎯-목표-설정" class="headerlink" title="🎯 목표 설정"></a>🎯 목표 설정</h2><p><strong>최종 목표:</strong></p><ul><li>8주 내 CKA (Certified Kubernetes Administrator) 취득</li><li>실무에서 바로 사용할 수 있는 K8s 운영 능력 확보</li><li>클라우드 네이티브 아키텍처 설계 역량 강화</li></ul><p><strong>학습 접근법:</strong></p><ul><li>이론 30% + 실습 70%의 hands-on 중심 학습</li><li>실제 운영 시나리오 기반 문제 해결</li><li>커뮤니티 활동을 통한 지식 공유</li></ul><span id="more"></span><h2 id="📅-8주-학습-계획"><a href="#📅-8주-학습-계획" class="headerlink" title="📅 8주 학습 계획"></a>📅 8주 학습 계획</h2><h3 id="Week-1-2-기초-다지기"><a href="#Week-1-2-기초-다지기" class="headerlink" title="Week 1-2: 기초 다지기"></a>Week 1-2: 기초 다지기</h3><p><strong>목표</strong>: Kubernetes 핵심 개념 완전 이해</p><p><strong>Day 1-3: 환경 구축</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 로컬 K8s 환경 구축</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 1. Docker Desktop Kubernetes 활성화</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 2. kubectl 설치 및 설정</span></span><br><span class="line">kubectl version --client</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 3. 실습용 클러스터 생성 (kind 사용)</span></span><br><span class="line">kind create cluster --name cka-practice</span><br><span class="line">kubectl cluster-info --context kind-cka-practice</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>Day 4-7: 핵심 리소스 마스터</strong></p><ul><li>Pod, ReplicaSet, Deployment</li><li>Service (ClusterIP, NodePort, LoadBalancer)</li><li>Ingress</li><li>ConfigMap, Secret</li><li>Namespace</li></ul><p><strong>실습 과제:</strong></p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># nginx-deployment.yaml</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">apiVersion:</span> <span class="string">apps/v1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">kind:</span> <span class="string">Deployment</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">metadata:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">nginx-deployment</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">namespace:</span> <span class="string">production</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">spec:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">replicas:</span> <span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">selector:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">matchLabels:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">app:</span> <span class="string">nginx</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">template:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">metadata:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">labels:</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">app:</span> <span class="string">nginx</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">spec:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">containers:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">nginx</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">image:</span> <span class="string">nginx:1.21</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">ports:</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">containerPort:</span> <span class="number">80</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">resources:</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">requests:</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">memory:</span> <span class="string">&quot;64Mi&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">cpu:</span> <span class="string">&quot;250m&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">limits:</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">memory:</span> <span class="string">&quot;128Mi&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">cpu:</span> <span class="string">&quot;500m&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Week-3-4-고급-기능-정복"><a href="#Week-3-4-고급-기능-정복" class="headerlink" title="Week 3-4: 고급 기능 정복"></a>Week 3-4: 고급 기능 정복</h3><p><strong>목표</strong>: 스토리지, 네트워킹, 보안 완전 정복</p><p><strong>학습 내용:</strong></p><ul><li>PersistentVolume, PersistentVolumeClaim</li><li>StorageClass (동적 프로비저닝)</li><li>NetworkPolicy (네트워크 보안)</li><li>RBAC (Role-Based Access Control)</li><li>SecurityContext, PodSecurityPolicy</li></ul><p><strong>실전 예제:</strong></p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># rbac-example.yaml</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">apiVersion:</span> <span class="string">v1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">kind:</span> <span class="string">ServiceAccount</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">metadata:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">pod-reader</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">namespace:</span> <span class="string">default</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">apiVersion:</span> <span class="string">rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">kind:</span> <span class="string">Role</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">metadata:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">namespace:</span> <span class="string">default</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">pod-reader</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">rules:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">apiGroups:</span> [<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>]</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">resources:</span> [<span class="string">&quot;pods&quot;</span>]</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">verbs:</span> [<span class="string">&quot;get&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;watch&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;list&quot;</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">---</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">apiVersion:</span> <span class="string">rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">kind:</span> <span class="string">RoleBinding</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">metadata:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">read-pods</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">namespace:</span> <span class="string">default</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">subjects:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">kind:</span> <span class="string">ServiceAccount</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">pod-reader</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">namespace:</span> <span class="string">default</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">roleRef:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">kind:</span> <span class="string">Role</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">pod-reader</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">apiGroup:</span> <span class="string">rbac.authorization.k8s.io</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Week-5-6-클러스터-운영-마스터"><a href="#Week-5-6-클러스터-운영-마스터" class="headerlink" title="Week 5-6: 클러스터 운영 마스터"></a>Week 5-6: 클러스터 운영 마스터</h3><p><strong>목표</strong>: 실제 운영 시나리오 완벽 대응</p><p><strong>핵심 스킬:</strong></p><ul><li>클러스터 업그레이드 (kubeadm)</li><li>etcd 백업 및 복구</li><li>로깅 및 모니터링 (Prometheus, Grafana)</li><li>트러블슈팅 (네트워크, 스토리지, 성능)</li></ul><p><strong>실습 시나리오:</strong></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># etcd 백업 (CKA 시험 필수!)</span></span><br><span class="line">ETCDCTL_API=3 etcdctl snapshot save /tmp/etcd-backup.db \</span><br><span class="line">  --endpoints=https://127.0.0.1:2379 \</span><br><span class="line">  --cacert=/etc/kubernetes/pki/etcd/ca.crt \</span><br><span class="line">  --cert=/etc/kubernetes/pki/etcd/server.crt \</span><br><span class="line">  --key=/etc/kubernetes/pki/etcd/server.key</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># etcd 복구</span></span><br><span class="line">ETCDCTL_API=3 etcdctl snapshot restore /tmp/etcd-backup.db \</span><br><span class="line">  --data-dir=/var/lib/etcd-backup \</span><br><span class="line">  --name=master \</span><br><span class="line">  --initial-cluster=master=https://127.0.0.1:2380 \</span><br><span class="line">  --initial-advertise-peer-urls=https://127.0.0.1:2380</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="Week-7-8-CKA-시험-집중-준비"><a href="#Week-7-8-CKA-시험-집중-준비" class="headerlink" title="Week 7-8: CKA 시험 집중 준비"></a>Week 7-8: CKA 시험 집중 준비</h3><p><strong>목표</strong>: 시험 통과를 위한 실전 연습</p><p><strong>시험 도메인별 집중 연습:</strong></p><ol><li><strong>클러스터 아키텍처, 설치 및 구성 (25%)</strong></li><li><strong>워크로드 및 스케줄링 (15%)</strong>  </li><li><strong>서비스 및 네트워킹 (20%)</strong></li><li><strong>스토리지 (10%)</strong></li><li><strong>트러블슈팅 (30%)</strong></li></ol><h2 id="📚-학습-리소스-추천"><a href="#📚-학습-리소스-추천" class="headerlink" title="📚 학습 리소스 추천"></a>📚 학습 리소스 추천</h2><h3 id="필수-자료-무료"><a href="#필수-자료-무료" class="headerlink" title="필수 자료 (무료)"></a>필수 자료 (무료)</h3><ol><li><strong>Kubernetes 공식 문서</strong>: <a href="https://kubernetes.io/docs/">https://kubernetes.io/docs/</a></li><li><strong>kubectl Cheat Sheet</strong>: 시험 중 참고 가능</li><li><strong>GitHub 실습 레포</strong>: 직접 만든 예제들</li></ol><h3 id="유료-강의-투자-가치-있음"><a href="#유료-강의-투자-가치-있음" class="headerlink" title="유료 강의 (투자 가치 있음)"></a>유료 강의 (투자 가치 있음)</h3><ol><li><strong>Udemy - Mumshad Mannambeth</strong>: “CKA with Practice Tests”</li><li><strong>A Cloud Guru</strong>: “Certified Kubernetes Administrator”</li><li><strong>Linux Foundation</strong>: 공식 CKA 교육과정</li></ol><h3 id="실습-환경-구성"><a href="#실습-환경-구성" class="headerlink" title="실습 환경 구성"></a>실습 환경 구성</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 1. 로컬 환경 (개발/학습용)</span></span><br><span class="line">kind create cluster --config=multi-node-config.yaml</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 2. 클라우드 환경 (실전 연습용)  </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># AWS EKS, GCP GKE, Azure AKS 중 선택</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 3. 가상머신 환경 (시험 환경과 동일)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># VirtualBox + Ubuntu로 3노드 클러스터 구성</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="✅-주간-성과-측정"><a href="#✅-주간-성과-측정" class="headerlink" title="✅ 주간 성과 측정"></a>✅ 주간 성과 측정</h2><h3 id="Week-1-체크리스트"><a href="#Week-1-체크리스트" class="headerlink" title="Week 1 체크리스트"></a>Week 1 체크리스트</h3><ul><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> kubectl 기본 명령어 50개 암기</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Pod 생성&#x2F;삭제&#x2F;수정 1분 내 완료</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Service로 Pod 노출 완벽 이해</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> ConfigMap&#x2F;Secret 실무 활용법</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> <strong>블로그 포스트</strong>: “Kubernetes 시작하기”</li></ul><h3 id="Week-2-체크리스트"><a href="#Week-2-체크리스트" class="headerlink" title="Week 2 체크리스트"></a>Week 2 체크리스트</h3><ul><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Deployment 롤링 업데이트 마스터</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Ingress 설정으로 외부 트래픽 라우팅</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Namespace 기반 멀티 테넌트 구성</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> <strong>블로그 포스트</strong>: “K8s 핵심 리소스 완전 정복”</li></ul><h3 id="Week-3-4-체크리스트"><a href="#Week-3-4-체크리스트" class="headerlink" title="Week 3-4 체크리스트"></a>Week 3-4 체크리스트</h3><ul><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> PV&#x2F;PVC 동적 프로비저닝 구현</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> RBAC으로 세밀한 권한 관리</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> NetworkPolicy로 마이크로세그멘테이션</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> <strong>블로그 포스트</strong>: “K8s 보안 설정 실전 가이드”</li></ul><h3 id="Week-5-6-체크리스트"><a href="#Week-5-6-체크리스트" class="headerlink" title="Week 5-6 체크리스트"></a>Week 5-6 체크리스트</h3><ul><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> etcd 백업&#x2F;복구 10회 이상 연습</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 클러스터 업그레이드 시나리오 완료</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 장애 상황 트러블슈팅 20개 케이스</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> <strong>블로그 포스트</strong>: “K8s 운영 중 만난 장애들”</li></ul><h3 id="Week-7-8-체크리스트"><a href="#Week-7-8-체크리스트" class="headerlink" title="Week 7-8 체크리스트"></a>Week 7-8 체크리스트</h3><ul><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> Killer.sh 모의시험 5회 이상 (80점 이상)</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> 시험 환경에서 실전 연습 완료</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> CKA 시험 접수 및 응시</li><li><input disabled="" type="checkbox"> <strong>블로그 포스트</strong>: “CKA 합격 후기 및 팁”</li></ul><h2 id="🎯-실무-적용-전략"><a href="#🎯-실무-적용-전략" class="headerlink" title="🎯 실무 적용 전략"></a>🎯 실무 적용 전략</h2><h3 id="사내-프로젝트-제안"><a href="#사내-프로젝트-제안" class="headerlink" title="사내 프로젝트 제안"></a>사내 프로젝트 제안</h3><p><strong>1단계: 기존 서비스 컨테이너화</strong></p><figure class="highlight dockerfile"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 기존 Spring Boot 애플리케이션</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">FROM</span> openjdk:<span class="number">11</span>-jre-slim</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">COPY</span><span class="language-bash"> target/app.jar app.jar</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">EXPOSE</span> <span class="number">8080</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">ENTRYPOINT</span><span class="language-bash"> [<span class="string">&quot;java&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;-jar&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;/app.jar&quot;</span>]</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>2단계: Kubernetes 매니페스트 작성</strong></p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># k8s/deployment.yaml</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">apiVersion:</span> <span class="string">apps/v1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">kind:</span> <span class="string">Deployment</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">metadata:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">spring-app</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">spec:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">replicas:</span> <span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">selector:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">matchLabels:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">app:</span> <span class="string">spring-app</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">template:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">metadata:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">labels:</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">app:</span> <span class="string">spring-app</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">spec:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">containers:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">app</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">image:</span> <span class="string">myregistry/spring-app:latest</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">ports:</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">containerPort:</span> <span class="number">8080</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">env:</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">SPRING_PROFILES_ACTIVE</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">value:</span> <span class="string">&quot;production&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">livenessProbe:</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">httpGet:</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">path:</span> <span class="string">/actuator/health</span></span><br><span class="line">            <span class="attr">port:</span> <span class="number">8080</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">initialDelaySeconds:</span> <span class="number">30</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">periodSeconds:</span> <span class="number">10</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>3단계: CI&#x2F;CD 파이프라인 구축</strong></p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># .github/workflows/deploy.yml</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Deploy</span> <span class="string">to</span> <span class="string">Kubernetes</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">on:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">push:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">branches:</span> [<span class="string">main</span>]</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">jobs:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">runs-on:</span> <span class="string">ubuntu-latest</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">steps:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">uses:</span> <span class="string">actions/checkout@v3</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Build</span> <span class="string">and</span> <span class="string">Push</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">run:</span> <span class="string">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">          docker build -t myregistry/spring-app:$&#123;&#123; github.sha &#125;&#125; .</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">          docker push myregistry/spring-app:$&#123;&#123; github.sha &#125;&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string"></span>      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Deploy</span> <span class="string">to</span> <span class="string">K8s</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">run:</span> <span class="string">|</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">          kubectl set image deployment/spring-app app=myregistry/spring-app:$&#123;&#123; github.sha &#125;&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">          kubectl rollout status deployment/spring-app</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="🚀-성공을-위한-팁"><a href="#🚀-성공을-위한-팁" class="headerlink" title="🚀 성공을 위한 팁"></a>🚀 성공을 위한 팁</h2><h3 id="학습-효율성-극대화"><a href="#학습-효율성-극대화" class="headerlink" title="학습 효율성 극대화"></a>학습 효율성 극대화</h3><ol><li><strong>매일 실습</strong>: 이론 30% + 실습 70%</li><li><strong>문제 해결 중심</strong>: 에러를 만나고 해결하는 경험</li><li><strong>커뮤니티 활용</strong>: Kubernetes Slack, Reddit 참여</li><li><strong>블로그 기록</strong>: 학습한 내용 즉시 포스팅</li></ol><h3 id="시험-합격-전략"><a href="#시험-합격-전략" class="headerlink" title="시험 합격 전략"></a>시험 합격 전략</h3><ol><li><strong>시간 관리</strong>: 문제당 평균 7분 배분</li><li><strong>kubectl 숙련도</strong>: 명령어 타이핑 속도 향상</li><li><strong>공식 문서 활용</strong>: 시험 중 참고 가능</li><li><strong>실전 연습</strong>: Killer.sh에서 반복 연습</li></ol><h3 id="실무-적용-포인트"><a href="#실무-적용-포인트" class="headerlink" title="실무 적용 포인트"></a>실무 적용 포인트</h3><ol><li><strong>점진적 도입</strong>: 작은 서비스부터 시작</li><li><strong>모니터링 우선</strong>: Prometheus + Grafana 필수</li><li><strong>보안 고려</strong>: RBAC, NetworkPolicy 적용</li><li><strong>문서화</strong>: 운영 가이드 작성</li></ol><h2 id="📈-다음-단계-계획"><a href="#📈-다음-단계-계획" class="headerlink" title="📈 다음 단계 계획"></a>📈 다음 단계 계획</h2><h3 id="CKA-취득-후-로드맵"><a href="#CKA-취득-후-로드맵" class="headerlink" title="CKA 취득 후 로드맵"></a>CKA 취득 후 로드맵</h3><ol><li><strong>CKAD (Developer)</strong> 취득</li><li><strong>CKS (Security)</strong> 취득</li><li><strong>클라우드별 전문 자격증</strong> (AWS EKS, GCP GKE)</li><li><strong>기술 리더십</strong> 역할 도전</li></ol><h3 id="장기적-커리어-발전"><a href="#장기적-커리어-발전" class="headerlink" title="장기적 커리어 발전"></a>장기적 커리어 발전</h3><ul><li><strong>플랫폼 엔지니어</strong>: 개발자 경험 플랫폼 구축</li><li><strong>클라우드 아키텍트</strong>: 멀티클라우드 전략 수립</li><li><strong>기술 리드</strong>: 팀 기술 방향성 결정</li><li><strong>DevOps 컨설턴트</strong>: 조직의 DevOps 문화 구축</li></ul><hr><p><strong>시작일</strong>: 오늘부터<br><strong>목표일</strong>: 8주 후 CKA 취득<br><strong>다음 포스트</strong>: “Kubernetes 실습 환경 구축하기”</p><p><em>함께 Kubernetes를 정복해봅시다! 궁금한 점이나 함께 스터디하고 싶으시면 댓글로 연락주세요.</em></p>]]></content>
      
      
